metadata.name: Jundo House | Gallant Member's Token
metadata.description:
Welcome!  

This is our version of a more exclusive member's token which is invitation only or referred to mint.

While every Jundo House friend shares in most community channels, irl events and such we did need some exclusivity for formality reasons when sharing more sensitive investment opportunities and correlating information e.g accreditation requirements, NDAs, data room content and formal business dealings. 

Our future angel / founder exclusive dinners and events will mandate this token role along with other *perks.  

Thanks for joining!
